  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0D9XxVETX4p1gFtPugOny155yPC9OdlJr20EYLQGETb1gQdhBicWIRfqw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505175495\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60639165&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0D9XxVETX4p1gFtPugOny155yPC9OdlJr20EYLQGETb1gQdhBicWIRfqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：peter东</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Deepmind推出的SIMA 2，让智能体能在虚拟环境（商业游戏）中，边聊天边进行复杂的多模态推理。作为具身通用智能的原型，SIMA 2已从静态数据集迈向无限程序化生成的训练场。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">游戏领域的进步，一直是可被视为迈向通用人工智能的前奏，从棋类到多人合作的即时战略游戏，例如星际争霸。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但之前的智能体在玩游戏的时候，需要程序开发者手动编程，2024年，Deepmind推出了SIMA（Scalable Instructable Multiworld Agent），允许智能体虚拟环境中遵循自然语言编写的指令，例如你可以通过提示词。让游戏角色前往虚拟环境中的某地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而近日新推出的SIMA 2，通过整合Gemini的多模态推理能力，让SIMA正从一个指令执行者演变为一个互动游戏伙伴。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SIMA 2不仅能够在虚拟世界中，遵循自然语言指令完成对应的操作，它现在还可以思考自己的目标，与用户对话，并随着时间的推移不断自我提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"275\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"488\" data-imgfileid=\"505175002\" data-ratio=\"0.48946840521564694\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"997\" data-width=\"997\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7632e39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5KgWKibflvibpEjUribOPMDEYE5E8DOjiazFOpppiaReEdQfkL1NYsL2GqKoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一个与你互动的游戏搭子</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比只能通过「查看」屏幕并使用虚拟键盘和鼠标，根据指令在固定游戏中执行对应操作的SIMA 1，SIMA 2的提升在于它不仅能够响应指令，还能够经由Gemini理解用户的目标，执行复杂推理以达成目标，并在游戏环境中熟练地进行目标导向的行为。这使得SIMA 2可以在它从未见过的游戏中完成任务，具体见下面视频对SIMA 1和SIMA 2的对比。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除了执行指令，SIMA 2还可以与用户多轮对话，一边推理自身行为及其所处环境，一边描述其意图执行的操作，并详细说明其完成目标的步骤。这使得与SIMA 2中智能体的互动，感觉更像是与一个能够理解当前任务的伙伴协作，而不是在下达命令。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"224\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"505175001\" data-ratio=\"0.399197592778335\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"997\" data-width=\"997\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a1e0aa41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5Kk0HMRBGCZZXHFlQmFiaYY8Mq0GJ9ffYhnGRb6rE9WaiamXZWFFqY6rTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图1：智能体-环境接口。智能体接收包含当前指令的提示。根据最近的帧进行条件建模，智能体输出内部推理、对话和动作，并在每一步指定要生成的模态类型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">SIMA的强大泛化能力</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">吹响迈向通用人工智能的号角</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">得益于Gemini模型本身的多模态特征，SIMA 2能够理解多模态的提示词，可以进行多语言的对话，甚至能理解表情包。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"269\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"478\" data-imgfileid=\"505175004\" data-ratio=\"0.4794383149448345\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"997\" data-width=\"997\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5fbe7858&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5KmQS7C9IYn6JQ3nEZrgEBp0Nb5SBNqqDdrZevNSTjF7zvgde3OfiapAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图2：SIMA 2 可以处理各种新颖且复杂的指令，包括分解指令以成功导航至特定房间。SIMA 2 还可以接受用户手绘的草图，以指定位置、路径或物体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"238\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"421\" data-imgfileid=\"505175003\" data-ratio=\"0.4226907630522088\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"996\" data-width=\"996\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f60cdbbf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5KKRvpzjmUujU3p8QZNib7Z3lkiaaGA0qJ7PD5Olibh1OtBUJ2JVyBtG6Vg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图3：通过使用Gemini，SIMA 2可以实现更复杂推理能力。例如上图的智能体成功利用复杂图表完成搭建营火的多步骤任务。整个过程中，智能体持续沟通其当前行为和下一步计划。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更关键的是，SIMA 2具有将所学概念迁移的能力。例如，在某一游戏中学到了如何「采矿」，而到了另一游戏中，就会用学到的技能来进行「采集」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样的迁移与泛化能力，是通用人工智能的基础。事实上，由于这种能力，SIMA 2在广泛的任务上的表现显著接近人类玩家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"216\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"287\" data-imgfileid=\"505175000\" data-ratio=\"0.38420348058902276\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"747\" data-width=\"747\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5640e4a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5KhkuLyddibTsy0sc1TcD7TvcYRic59LmfwGgkkZ3HPPC8lP8YbVC3vOJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图4：在所有训练游戏环境中中，SIMA 1、SIMA 2 和人类的任务完成成功率对比，SIMA 2相比SIMA 1平均成功率翻倍，在人类和自动评估时下均接近人类水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"390\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"692\" data-imgfileid=\"505175006\" data-ratio=\"0.6940822467402207\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"997\" data-width=\"997\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54082519&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5KIcSwblE5M6K4zura6mPPUNCsbfGrtuh32zibeeHial5ujPQRvBq7ibgpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图5：SIMA 2在多个技能类别中显著优于 SIMA 1。在交互和物体管理等类别中，SIMA 2的表现几乎接近人类水平。然而，在资源收集和战斗等其他类别中，SIMA 2 仍有提升空间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了测试 SIMA 2 的泛化能力极限，Deepmind的研究者将其与 Genie 3 结合使用，Genie 3 可以根据单个图像或文本提示实时生成新的 3D 模拟世界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当SIMA 2在这些新生成的世界中进行挑战时，发现它能够合理地定位自身，理解用户指令，并朝着目标采取有意义的行动，尽管它从未见过这些环境。它展现出了前所未有的适应能力。例如下面视频中，SIMA 2能够引导蝴蝶在Genie 3生成的全新环境中，导航找到红色的花朵。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">可扩展的、多任务的自我提升</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SIMA 2最令人兴奋的新功能之一是其自我提升的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在训练过程中，SIMA 2中的智能体通过试错，以及将Gemini给的反馈作为指导，能够执行越来越复杂和新颖的任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，在最初从人类给的演示中学习之后，SIMA 2 可以通过自主游戏在新游戏中学习，无需额外示例，就能在之前未见过的世界中提升游戏技能。在后续训练中，SIMA 2 自己的经验数据可以用于训练下一个甚至更强大的智能体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">类似下围棋的Alpha-zero能够在完全不看人类棋谱的时候完成训练。研究者甚至能够利用 SIMA 2的自我提升能力Genie新创建的环境中进行训练，这将是向在多样化生成世界中训练通用智能体的重要一步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1458\" data-imgfileid=\"505175007\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2592\" data-width=\"2592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0bffc8f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5Kb8iatJJ2qfyRod5WWLicuTNRHv2ejZic2s7oH7SQQPcN4LmwbeibLOuQzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图6：SIMA 2的自我提升循环始于Gemini为SIMA 2提供一个初始任务和对行为的奖励估计。这些信息随后被添加到自生成经验库中，该经验库用于后续版本的进一步训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种迭代改进的良性循环为未来铺平了道路，届时智能体可以在极少的人类干预下学习和成长，成为具身智能中的开放性学习者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"408\" data-backw=\"478\" data-height=\"408\" data-imgfileid=\"505175005\" data-ratio=\"0.8535564853556485\" style=\"width: 338px;height: 289px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"478\" data-width=\"478\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4513357a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3421JoKBcNN2GZW2B2ct5KaZiaDsiaDsoib2RyeEI6KpNUqdHjUNIGZNV3pibTggiclTPROP0PqhQiaDNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图7：在固定任务集上，SIMA 2的性能稳步提升，逐渐接近，甚至在某些情况下超过了人类的得分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">由于可以在多种游戏环境中，执行复杂的推理和操作，并通过自主游戏持续学习，SIMA 2是迈向人工通用智能（AGI）迈进的重要一步，对机器人技术和通用AI智能体的未来发展具有重要意义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SIMA 2的出现，说明了借助多样化的多世界数据和Gemini等大模型强大的推理能力，可以成功地将许多特有系统的功能统一到一个连贯的通用智能智能体中，这为机器人领域的应用提供了强有力的方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能体在虚拟环境中所学到的技能，从导航和工具使用到协作任务执行，都会是未来物理世界中 AI 助手所需技能的基本构建模块。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，研究者也承认，SIMA 2中的智能体在处理超长时间跨度、复杂的任务时，仍然面临需要大量多步骤推理和目标验证等挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，SIMA 2 对交互历史的记忆相对较短。智能体必须使用有限的上下文窗口来实现低延迟的交互。而且通过键盘和鼠标界面执行精确的低级操作，以及在复杂的3D场景中实现稳健的视觉理解，仍然是整个领域持续探索的开放性挑战。 &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://x.com/jparkerholder/status/2000543389918339412?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/jparkerholder/status/2000543389918339412?s=20</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepMind 发布 SIMA 2，一个结合 Gemini 多模态推理的具身通用智能体，能在商业游戏中自主学习、泛化和自我提升，迈向 AGI。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepMind 发布 SIMA 2，一个结合 Gemini 多模态推理的具身通用智能体，能在商业游戏中自主学习、泛化和自我提升，迈向 AGI。",
  "summary": "DeepMind 发布了其具身通用智能原型 SIMA 2，这是一个能在虚拟环境（商业游戏）中，通过多模态推理实现“感知-推理-行动-反思”闭环的智能体。SIMA 2 整合了 Gemini 的多模态推理能力，使其不仅能遵循自然语言指令，还能理解用户目标、进行复杂推理、与用户对话并自我提升。它展示了强大的泛化能力，能将在一个游戏中学习到的技能迁移到另一个游戏中，并在广泛任务上的表现接近人类水平。文章强调了 SIMA 2 在多样化世界中自主学习和自我提升的能力，为实现人工通用智能（AGI）和在机器人领域的实际应用奠定了基础。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "SIMA 2 是一个具身通用智能原型，能够打通“感知-推理-行动-反思”的闭环。",
      "explanation": "SIMA 2 通过整合 Gemini 的多模态推理能力，使其在虚拟环境（商业游戏）中不仅能遵循指令，还能理解深层目标，进行复杂推理，互动对话并自我改进。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SIMA 2 具备强大的泛化和迁移学习能力。",
      "explanation": "它能够将在一个游戏中学到的技能（如“采矿”）泛化并迁移到其他游戏中的类似任务（如“采集”），这对于通用人工智能的发展至关重要。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SIMA 2 实现了自我提升的训练机制。",
      "explanation": "智能体通过试错和 Gemini 提供的反馈进行学习，能够自主在新环境中提升游戏技能，甚至利用自我生成的经验数据来训练更强大的后续版本，类似于 AlphaZero 的自学习过程。"
    },
    {
